RELEASE NOTES for BANDIT
========================

This is the release "1.4.1" of the BANDIT toolkit.
This is a "STABLE" release.

Visit https://phy.wiki for more information.


MAJOR CHANGES in 1.4.1
======================

* Allow bundles not to update system databases after installation
* Allow editing the description file of a bundle as well as the configuration file
* Do no prepare package sources on fetch or download

